Template: kaltura-alertmanager/smtp_host
Type: string
Default: localhost:25
Description: The SMTP server to send alerts through:

Template: kaltura-alertmanager/from_addr
Type: string
Description: Alertmanager's from address

Template: kaltura-alertmanager/smtp_user
Type: string
Default: 
Description: The SMTP user [leave empty if no auth is required]:

Template: kaltura-alertmanager/smtp_passwd
Type: string
Default: 
Description: The SMTP user's password [leave empty if no auth is required]:

Template: kaltura-alertmanager/default_alerting_email_addr
Type: string
Default: 
Description: Email address:
	The default email address to send alerts to. Additional addresses and sending conditions can be declared by editing /opt/kaltura/prometheus/alertmanager/etc/alertmanager.yml 
